12 DAYS OF GIVEAWAYS! 

DAY 5: We're excited to partner with @chrissandersart to give away this Loungefly Disney Lilo & Stitch bundle to one lucky winner! 

To enter: 

1. Follow @chrissandersart & @loungefly 
2. Like & save this post. 
3. Tag 2 friends that love Stitch! 
Bonus: Share to your stories and tag @chrissandersart & @loungefly

 *Ends 12/19 at 11:59pm PST, US only. The winner will be chosen randomly and will receive a DM confirmation. ⚠️ Please check that the DM is from the officially verified, correctly spelled @loungefly account. Never share your information with anyone claiming to be us. There will never be a link to click on to claim your prize.

Tweeterhead is proud to announce that we are teaming up with the amazing artist, director, and visionary, Chris Sanders, to continue his incredible statue collection based on his original characters!

Over the years Chris has designed whimsical pieces of his own creations, and we couldn't be more excited to expand our offerings by helping produce them and continue that collection - Mermaids, Witches, and other awesome things, OH MY!
.
.

Tweeterhead is ecstatic to keep working with Chris Sanders on continuing his artist series line and offering a new edition of his beautiful mermaid, Nimue!

For this new Second Edition, we went back to the original digital sculpt file, with sculptor Anders Ehrenborg, and completely re-worked almost every aspect of this piece - Lots of subtle changes to her portrait, anatomy, and tail, as well as re-working the base and a completely new shark! And the paint has been updated as well!

We're hoping this makes collectors of the original piece happy, as well as people who missed out on her originally so they can finally snag her as well!

More info for her coming soon, and please RSVP over at sideshow.com 
.
.
.
#tweeterhead #chrissandersart #chrissanders #mermaid #nimue #madebytweeterhead #distributedbysideshowcollectibles

Tweeterhead Presents the new Nimue “Second Edition” Statue by Chris Sanders and Anders Ehrenborg! Everyone’s favorite mermaid is back, updated, and available once again!
.
This Nimue Statue measures roughly 7” tall, 6.5” wide and 6.5” deep when fully assembled - from the bottom of the base to the top of the flower in her hair, to the furthest out points on the statue.

This fully sculpted polyresin statue comes placed in her fun underwater environment with her cute little sea friends, and a few small updates from the original edition! We went back to the original digital sculpt file and completely re-worked almost every aspect of this piece. Lots of subtle changes to her portrait, anatomy, and tail, as well as re-working the base a tiny bit and including a new shark buddy! And the paint has been updated overall as well! We're hoping this makes collectors of the original Nimue happy, as well as people who missed out on her originally!
.
There is no Exclusive Edition with this piece, just the Standard Version.
.
The Nimue “Second Edition” will have an Edition Size TBD, will retail for $300 USD, and is ready for preorder NOW at Tweeterhead.com:
.
https://tweeterhead.com/product/nimue/
.
If you purchase from Tweeterhead and pay in full, buyers will get $25 off! We will only be selling in the continental US, and all international buyers can still get her from our good friends at Sideshow!
.
https://www.sideshow.com/collectibles/chris-sanders-nimue-second-edition-tweeterhead-911499
.
Artist Credits: Chris Sanders (Design), Anders Ehrenborg (Sculpt), Liz Maggie (Paint)
.

Tweeterhead’s Re-issue of our popular Nimue figurine is available for pre-order right now!

For #MerMay, we actually have a mermaid! So step into this whimsical world with the Nimue Statue designed by artist extraordinaire, Chris Sanders! Get an exclusive peek at the adorable 3D sculpt in all its glory by the crazy talented sculptor, Anders Ehrenborg! Pre-order this magical lil beauty right now at https://tweeterhead.com/product/nimue/

With its charming stylized features, and a touch of nautical playfulness, it's an absolute must-have for collectors of all types!
